channel.description:
Ok Guys So I Decided To Release My 660 RSPS Not many people use 660's anymore but i thought why not release it , i have put hard work into this whether you think its a leech or not, If you don't having anything nice to say don't say anything but feel free to tell me what i should and shouldn't have done ! What I've Added : - NEX - NEW HOME - LOYALTY TITLE - NEW COMBAT - GENERAL GRADOR (BANDOS BOSS) - Kree'ara or whatever (Armadyl Boss) + Heaps More SOURCE : http://www.upload.ee/files/2752472/RuneIntense-FusionX_RELEASE.7z.html Client: http://www.upload.ee/files/2752476/RuneIntense_CLIENT_RELEASE.7z.html CACHE : Put In Your User File [ EXAMPLE C:\Users\[USER FILE] <--- For Windows 7) LINK : http://uppit.com/1299ggqizygj/.rspsCache2.zip
